race.comment: INCANTATA (10) chased in vain behind DREAM INHERIT last time when sent out favourite. Meets the winner better this time and can turn the tables. DREAM INHERIT (2) proved too sharp for them last start when leading all the way here for a dominant win. Goes up in the weights but is sure to push forward again from her wide draw and take plenty of reeling in. FAIRNESS IS BEST (4) hasn't won for a very long time but has shown signs of life in his last two. Drawn well and is worth keeping safe. GOLD CANDLE (9) broke the maiden in style here last start when working home over the top of them. Will drift back again from the wide draw and be saved for the final shot at them.
